<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>導向至綠界付款頁面...</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: sans-serif;
      text-align: center;
      padding-top: 80px;
      background-color: #f7f7f7;
      color: #333;
    }
    .loader {
      margin: 20px auto;
      border: 6px solid #f3f3f3;
      border-top: 6px solid #00a0e9;
      border-radius: 50%;
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      animation: spin 1s linear infinite;
    }
    @keyframes spin {
      0% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
      100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h2>正在為您準備綠界付款頁面...</h2>
  <div class="loader"></div>
  <p>若未自動跳轉，請稍候或刷新頁面。</p>

  <%- html %>
</body>
</html>
